@startuml SD-12_Organization_Switching

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName "Arial"
skinparam defaultFontSize 17
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam dpi 300

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #555555
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
    FontStyle plain
}
skinparam actor {
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #555555
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
}
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #333333
    ArrowThickness 1
    ArrowFontColor #000000
    ArrowFontSize 16
    LifeLineBorderColor #333333
    LifeLineBorderThickness 1
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    GroupBodyBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
    GroupBorderColor #888888
    GroupBorderThickness 1
    GroupHeaderFontColor #000000
    DividerBackgroundColor #E8E8E8
    DividerFontColor #000000
    DividerBorderColor #AAAAAA
    DividerBorderThickness 1
    ParticipantBorderThickness 1
}
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    BorderColor #999999
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
}

actor       "User"       as User
participant "Web UI"     as UI
participant "Controller" as Ctrl
participant "Service"    as Svc
database    "Database"   as DB

' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Switch Organization (Client-Side Only) ==
' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

User -> UI : Click org in dropdown
UI   -> UI : switchOrg(orgId)
note right of UI
  1. Write orgId to localStorage
  2. Notify auth listeners
  3. Clear React Query cache
  4. router.push("/overview")
end note
UI  --> User : Redirect to /overview

' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== API Requests Scoped to New Org ==
' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

UI   -> Ctrl : GET /api/assets\nx-org-id: <newOrgId>
activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Svc  : inject orgId from header
Svc  -> DB   : query scoped to orgId
DB  --> Svc  : result
Svc --> Ctrl : data
Ctrl --> UI  : 200 OK
deactivate Ctrl
UI  --> User : Dashboard shows new org

' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Create New Organization ==
' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

User -> UI   : Enter name, click "Create"
UI   -> Ctrl : POST /api/organizations
activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Svc  : createOrganization(userId, dto)
activate Svc
Svc  -> DB   : save(Organization)
DB  --> Svc  : savedOrg
Svc  -> DB   : save(Member, role: ADMIN)
DB  --> Svc  : member
Svc --> Ctrl : organization
deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> UI  : 201 Created
deactivate Ctrl
UI  --> User : New org active

@enduml
